ms and owns  of agatha christie limited investor relations wwwrljentertainmentcom   the rlj companies all rights reserved  bethesda metro center suite  bethesda md  tel  sitemap acorn productions  an rlj entertainment inc company home foyles war production coventures press  news contact an rlj entertainment company acorn productions limited manages and licenses the rights of eminent crime mystery and drama brands including tv series foyles war we produce and coproduce tv and films based on the brands that we own and license the rights to publishing houses theatrical producers tv producers games developers and digital businesses throughout the world   sitemap   rlj entertainment inc image entertainment  wikipedia image entertainment from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from rlj entertainment jump to navigation search this article needs additional citations for verification please help improve this article by adding citations to reliable sources unsourced material may be challenged and removed december  learn how and when to remove this template message image entertainment type subsidiary industry entertainment founded   years ago  headquarters chatsworth california united states key people miguel penella ceo drew wilson cfo bill bromiley cao products dvd bluray digital video cd digital audio motion picture studio parent rlj entertainment website wwwimageentertainmentcom usrljentertainmentcom image entertainment inc is an american independent licensee producer and distributor of entertainment programming and film and television productions in north america with approximately  exclusive dvd titles and approximately  exclusive cd titles in domestic release and approximately  programs internationally via sublicense agreements for many of its titles image has exclusive audio and broadcast rights as well as digital download rights to approximately  video programs and over  audio programs containing more than  tracks the company is headquartered in chatsworth c